<h3>Position</h3>
<p>Positioning was achieved by using the ultrasonic sensor array in combination with an IMU. The IMU could produce
    gyroscopic and acceleration data. With a gyroscope, the roll, pitch, and yaw could be calculated. With the
    acceleration data, the position could be calculated using the double integral of the acceleration data.</p>

